Required attribution
--------------------
When you use, share, or adapt the Indexes, credit:

    Cerdeira L, Holt KE. "Dragon Indexes for AllTheBacteria and bacterial reference
    databases." London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine, 2026.
    DOI: «10.5281/zenodo.XXXXXXX»

Scope and carve-outs
--------------------
* This CC-BY-4.0 license applies to the INDEX DATA only. The Dragon SOFTWARE is licensed
  separately (MIT OR Apache-2.0) — see the repository root.
* The Indexes are derived from third-party source databases that retain their own licenses.
  See NOTICE.md for per-source attribution and terms.
* NOT all reference databases are redistributed here. In particular CARD (and, pending
  confirmation, VFDB) are NOT included due to their usage terms — build those indexes
  locally with the scripts in `scripts/`. See NOTICE.md.

CC-BY-4.0 is offered for the components we are entitled to redistribute (AllTheBacteria/
INSDC-derived genome indexes, GTDB, the per-species indexes, AMRFinderPlus, PlasmidFinder).
It permits commercial and clinical use, requiring only attribution.
